  <brief_title>Study to Evaluate the Efficacy of ALKS 3831 on Body Weight in Young Adults Who Have Been Recently Diagnosed With Schizophrenia, Schizophreniform, or Bipolar I Disorder</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Study to Evaluate the Effect of ALKS 3831 Compared to Olanzapine on Body Weight in Young Adults With Schizophrenia, Schizophreniform, or Bipolar I Disorder Who Are Early in Their Illness</official_title>
